{"tid":461574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何驅趕壁虎","createTime":"2017-11-07T17:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T16:03:27.000Z","uid":7430,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"008d4b528343ca04dc92f2d407e57501f6b924d4","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"[black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係等佢地唔好入屋 唔係整死佢 唔想執屍<br />\n<br />\n唔好話佢係益蟲神獸 因為我就係怕</span></span>[/black]<br />\n<br />\n買左部金剛2000 都仲走入黎<br />\n我就黎心臟病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb76371efa9dffe4aae70b3601255b128a599d","tid":461574,"uid":3625,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"咁得意都要趕"},{"pid":"256ecb620f6764b3aa20e71b59f75aa4ee36ec10","tid":461574,"uid":838,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"引堆甲由入屋<br />\n<br />\n只要個量夠多就可以嚇走哂啲壁虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541a497857c23327d62f4d20aa7bec9949624f49","tid":461574,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"買另一層樓啦"},{"pid":"4a4f3e3a8b764d7b7418aed384734e77e03dc87a","tid":461574,"uid":131980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"幫手食昆蟲，趕走佢做咩。"},{"pid":"7d391618335a7b975eb62cfde7fe938e91f0acbc","tid":461574,"uid":105935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"我寧願要佢 幫手食小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25837bd55be42fb58531e045a34e7a8b131428a2","tid":461574,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"好cute喎，我屋企都有"},{"pid":"2afa1c80b8a431776ae45cedda11526f737a0d1c","tid":461574,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"佢見到樓主你之後仲驚過你<br />\n直頭嚇到佢鼻哥窿都冇肉<br />\n樓主你又有冇諗過隻壁虎既感受"},{"pid":"aef8c8b71bcd357d626b702f2c712cfff757873c","tid":461574,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢係益蟲神獸</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fcd6a77b643469ba4cf888fe76602d9acb908ee","tid":461574,"uid":75735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:28:06.000Z","msg":"送比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7715166b5d8302bfe31b20d57978bd6ab2e2297","tid":461574,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"以前好驚<br />\n慢慢就慣"},{"pid":"1c652ef59e0d04ecd703c640b65e46dd95c22fbb","tid":461574,"uid":51171,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"信錯大家，屋企班仆街鹽蛇 蟲唔撚食，爬上飯枱食鳩我啲水果、飯餸(遲返去食屋企人留左啲餸俾我，一開燈班仆街就眼金金停係到，屌你老母真心嬲，俾佢地爬完仲點撚食，全部倒撚晒)，幾次都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n而家見一隻殺一隻，用拖鞋打撚到班仆街變漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、用熱水淥鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fea12f033f1ed666cb94bd764ebfff5761f2ba","tid":461574,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"成日亂鳩咁痾屎仲係門到夾死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985b1ae85be379cc4c752c43af9ff4e662b63405","tid":461574,"uid":111175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:40:28.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d313bc0230722360a6e4608f2ef0e078505349cd","tid":461574,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"食到冇野食就走。唔走既檢討下你屋企有咩留住佢"},{"pid":"dbdd790f58b3f83746efcaa545a52623169d4247","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食到冇野食就走。唔走既檢討下你屋企有咩留住佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依度附近有好多草樹<br />\n屋企無見過蟲 無蚊 <br />\n依10日見過一次小強就無<br />\n住高樓大廈既唔會明"},{"pid":"3bc50f14311f3583038388433c2322a0a759ac73","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信錯大家，屋企班仆街鹽蛇 蟲唔撚食，爬上飯枱食鳩我啲水果、飯餸(遲返去食屋企人留左啲餸俾我，一開燈班仆街就眼金金停係到，屌你老母真心嬲，俾佢地爬完仲點撚食，全部倒撚晒)，幾次都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n而家見一隻殺一隻，用拖鞋打撚到班仆街變漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、用熱水淥鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔敢整死佢地<br />\n佢地一行我就會進入恐懼狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba320255b65aafc35dae36f76d151987dc56ccf6","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢見到樓主你之後仲驚過你<br />\n直頭嚇到佢鼻哥窿都冇肉<br />\n樓主你又有冇諗過隻壁虎既感受</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有無諗過我感受<br />\n我就黎嚇到暈 <br />\n我一見佢地就瞓唔著 好似依家咁<br />\n我想瞓啊仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44ac12316c8559e3da59ad09d2fbc1ff7c98b52","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我寧願要佢 幫手食小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線 小強用殺蟲水一噴就死<br />\n壁虎都唔知點殺"},{"pid":"3c894621ddc8fde6c6b65b6ee351d0c7e2533d08","tid":461574,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T19:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁得意都要趕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明既 口味唔同<br />\n但我一啲都唔覺 仲好怕佢地<br />\n覺得佢地好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65184abc9e0f12c9a9f90ce10946a07f2fe75970","tid":461574,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"我屋企有鹽蛇就從來都無小強"},{"pid":"2337dcb9581f57fb0390bfd6cb226b692f92cd3b","tid":461574,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"X2 超煩<br />\n有時夜晚起身倒水比佢地嚇撚死<br />\n咁都算<br />\n成日係D暗位無啦啦自己死左<br />\n之後隔幾日聞到有腐屍味,搵極都極唔到條屍<br />\n宜家又有臭味啦,條屍都未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9987d6da529d8a8bfa1b394028d632a364322adf","tid":461574,"uid":73490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"買返條蛇勊住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b714a91914339c3438a427416baa2a6804d68a","tid":461574,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n擺啲臭丸喺啲櫃罅度<br />\n佢地唔鍾意臭丸陣味"},{"pid":"324863cf8b9a04511dfa6fa8f5d5d50a4af5f1c1","tid":461574,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"火攻"}]}